author: Sara Harris (sharris@sportingnews.com)
title: Padres' Petco Park is completely flooded
text:
February 28, 2017 10:57am EST February 28, 2017 10:57am EST The San Diego Padres need a boat right now to access the outfield of Petco Park. (Getty Images) 
Updated at 10:57 a.m. ET 
Updated at 10:57 a.m. ET 
The San Diego Padres need a boat right now to access the outfield of Petco Park. 
The stadium is completely flooded. This is insane. I lived in San Diego for 7 yrs & never saw anything like this. Petco Park under water. Be safe my San Diego friends! @Padres pic.twitter.com/YWKz7tHaBY
